    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1893-04-10T23:59:59-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1893-04-10T00:00:00-05:00" n="496"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d496">
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Mr. <persName type="from">Gresham</persName> to Mr. <persName
                            type="to">Hicks</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1893-04-10">
                            <hi rend="italic">April 10, 1893</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Mr. Gresham expresses gratification at the promises made by the Government of
                    Peru in regard to the incident at Mollendo and the confidence with which it is
                    expected these promises will be speedily fulfilled. He directs him to report on
                    that point.</p>
            </div>
